        {
            "title": "阿奴廷當選泰國總理 有助暫時緩解政治危機",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"阿努廷攝影師：Dario Pignatelli/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9j2TxBNeWyn9VBMxEWDERg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0dbd30136efee3a5e0e548c8758de78f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">阿努廷攝影師：Dario Pignatelli/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 泰國議會周五選舉阿阿努廷·參威拉恭為總理，他將成為自2023年以來泰國第三位總理。這一結果可能只會帶來短暫的政治平靜期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">58歲的阿努廷在議會下議院至少獲得250票，超過了獲勝所需的247票。他的挑戰者猜甲森·尼提西裡獲得了118票。截至曼谷時間下午3時51分，投票仍在進行之中。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位前建築業巨頭之所以能當選，得益於他得到了民主派人民黨的支持，人民黨要求他承諾在幾個月內舉行大選。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">之前報導：泰國議會下院即將選舉總理 保守派政治家阿奴廷勢將當選 (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Anutin Elected New Thai Prime Minister as Political Crisis Eases</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Pathom Sangwongwanich、Anuchit Nguyen、Eduard Gismatullin.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
